| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4295 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 34bfcf97-6f9c-57dd-83c7-eb1f8ac8736e"
